{
    "text": "\ud83d\udccd Wharton Beach, Esperance   We were told we missed out big time when we didn\u2019t visit this beach on our first lap of Australia, now we can understand why!   Make sure to visit if you\u2019re travelling to Esperance, it\u2019s a bit of a trek out of town but there\u2019s heaps of camping nearby and seeing those blues in person is definitely worth the drive \ud83d\ude0d  Make sure you SAVE this post if you\u2019re planning your own Australia travels and follow @jack.and.megan for more bucket list locations! \u2022 \u2022 \u2022 #wathedreamstate #visitwesternaustralia #seeaustralia_wa #esperance #australiasgoldenoutback #bucketlisttravel #travelbucketlist #beautifuldestinations #beach",
